column2: Open source eBook for nodejs - written w/ markdown, outputs to various formats (pdf, mobi, epub, html, etc)

column5:
Merge pull request #18 from grantheaslip/master

Fixed some typos, cleaned up awkward/unclear sentences
final spell checking and some slight rewording
rough drafts of asynch and stats

Removed EventEmitter.call(this) remove events chapter

No longer needed as emit() etc will check if this._events is
an object, if not it will be created

Added cover

I would imagine the dimensions would change per device,
so I have no clue what to use :) at least this beats the regular
calibre thing
Added mobi and epub to `make all`
Adding EPUB and MOBI support (requires calibres)
Adding static version of book in mobi format
